            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Joined my nephew in this school as we thought of choosing the best Muslim school. Here hostel & food are good. Importance for sports & Extra co-curricular are great. Prayers are followed strictly here. Staffs are good except 1 or 2. But if you think about studies, sorry to say you all that this school doesn't gives importance to studies. Speaking to the principal, he says that if you chose the school for studies, he regrets that this school is a bad choice that too explaining in front of the parents. Complaining about staffs on their teaching style doesn't mind him at all. So, parents who are all choosing this school, please don't waste your money if you opt for academic results of your children. Apart from studies, all are best in terms of protection, security, food and lodging. The principal doesn't realize that education is also more important nowadays in this advanced world. Office staffs in admin department behaves rudely. Finally, this school is no worth of spending lakhs of money for your children's future. Best of luck!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
